{"tid":367774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"照現在形勢，香港得番遊行靜坐唔洗坐監。","createTime":"2017-08-21T04:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T04:34:06.000Z","uid":26619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7bdb941c1fdb8184494a1a889fe434a344f130","tid":367774,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"根本政府都想打壓，任何形式抗爭。<br />\n現在香港大家坐一條船，重你打我打？<br />\n廿三條通過，你班熱青城連網上勇武都無機會。<br />\n今日重講緊風涼話，良心何在？<br />\n<br />\n你地講熱狗，言某係燒車，先坐4年，<br />\n燒車時重唔理身邊有其他抗爭者。<br />\n無炸死佢算佢好彩。"},{"pid":"be1bb171eb36807705d3a254366bca0f26daed18","tid":367774,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"時機未到"},{"pid":"613600b8cf685e821eef8ccaf1627e9e5f2b460e","tid":367774,"uid":73969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:31:31.000Z","msg":"聽日記得返工"},{"pid":"277cacbd6556f96d30fa3d2297370651aaed6e94","tid":367774,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"佢地咪係爬入公民廣場靜坐囉"}]}